item.title: My First Post
item.description: Introduction :::info You are reading the documentation for Vue 3! Vue 2 support has ended on Dec 31, 2023. Learn more about Vue 2 EOL. Upgrading from Vue 2? Check out the Migration Guide. ::: What is Vue? Vue (pronounced /vjuÀê/, like view) is a JavaScript framework for building user interfaces. It builds on top of standard HTML, CSS, and JavaScript and provides a declarative, component-based programming model that helps you efficiently develop user interfaces of any complexity.
